# 📝 Node.js To-Do List App

A simple To-Do list app built using **Node.js**, **JavaScript**, and **Tailwind CSS**.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Add new tasks
- Edit existing tasks
- Delete tasks
- Task data stored in a file (`todo.json`)

---

## 📦 Tech Stack
- Node.js (Backend)
- HTML & Tailwind CSS (Frontend)
- Vanilla JavaScript (DOM)

---

## 🛠 How to Run the App Locally

1. Clone this repo or download it  
2. Open the terminal inside the folder  
3. Run the server:

```bash
node server.js
